{"tid":2382170,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"香港/外國/回流/想認識香港 等緊你入嚟","createTime":"2021-01-27T06:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T03:20:05.000Z","uid":9178,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d815cbedb235e38f2c6146e5a4eea8326dda511e","tid":2382170,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:01:25.000Z","msg":"逐步會轉去signal 稍安勿躁 比啲時間大家適應 互相遷就<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">香港人<br />\n喺外國嘅香港人<br />\n回流香港嘅香港人<br />\n非香港人但想了解香港嘅人（eg 台灣）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個谷都歡迎你 希望大家可以知道更多唔同嘅野 識到更多朋友<br />\n<br />\n不論你好悶，係外國冇人傾計，返嚟香港後冇朋友，外國朋友想認識香港文化，呢到都十分啱你<br />\n<br />\n呢到絕不強逼你出聚，自由出聚。但強逼你吹水 唔出聚唔會踢 唔出聲會踢 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">谷內混合唔同國家嘅人（多數歐洲+香港+少量台灣人想認識香港）</span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗擔心時差，總有人陪到你<br />\n唔會揀人加，但set咗只可以填一次，所以要登入<br />\n擔心嘅，唔好加入<br />\n加人速度慢 要耐心等等<br />\n<br />\n#只係一個普通吹水谷 咁大個人 咩應該講 咩唔應該講 你自己知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/gnsgfxkgu6Lqyjew9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fgnsgfxkgu6Lqyjew9&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b12cc905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/gnsgfxkgu6Lqyjew9</a>"},{"pid":"16f07328ec674f9f4059045178e572dc41534e6d","tid":2382170,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6053ab2c9c6d56ffa656fbe6b216551f3e3a4b1d","tid":2382170,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee869ba14b20d59e0d798d6a0d8ae49df59c3c7","tid":2382170,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876a71f368bd165fb9f885f23471caf7c328efbe","tid":2382170,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27